  "excerpt": "For some upcoming projects, I got a chance to visit the Varga Store headquarters. I first fell in love with their location in Santa Monica many years ago when walking along Main Street. Now I love their shop in my…",
  "legacyPath": "/blog/2014/11/fashion-friday-2",
